  nobody even noticed.

  23 Nov 2003; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>; synaptics-0.12.0.ebuild:
  Re-marking as testing, it's not allowed to depend on something unstable.

  23 Nov 2003; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>; synaptics-0.12.0.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

